{
  "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
  "id": "sql-expression-multi-source-build-base-queries",
  "title": "Build two base queries",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "SQL expressions operate on the results of other queries. You need at least two queries to JOIN. In this milestone, you create a panel with Mixed data source and add two TestData queries that simulate different backends.\n\nTo build the base queries, complete the following steps:"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "autoCollapse": false,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/dashboards']",
          "content": "Click **Dashboards** in the left-side menu.",
          "requirements": ["navmenu-open"]
        },
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "Click **New** and select **New Dashboard**.",
          "requirements": ["on-page:/dashboards"],
          "steps": [
            { "action": "button", "reftarget": "New" },
            { "action": "highlight", "reftarget": "a[href='/dashboard/new']" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "noop",
          "content": "Click **+ Add visualization**. If you see an **Add** drawer instead, click the **Panel** card.\n\nThe panel editor opens."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source']",
          "content": "Click the **Data source** dropdown and search for `Mixed`.",
          "targetvalue": "Mixed",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "noop",
          "content": "Select **Mixed** from the results."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='query-editor-row']:first-child input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source']",
          "content": "In query row **A**, select **grafana-testdata-datasource**.",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "[aria-label='Test Data Query scenario select container']",
          "content": "Set the **Scenario** to **CSV Content** and paste the following data:\n\n```\ntime,host,cpu\n2025-01-01T00:00:00Z,web-1,45\n2025-01-01T01:00:00Z,web-2,72\n2025-01-01T02:00:00Z,web-1,38\n2025-01-01T03:00:00Z,web-3,91\n2025-01-01T04:00:00Z,web-2,65\n```",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='data-testid query-tab-add-query']",
          "content": "Click **Add query** to add a second query row."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='query-editor-row']:last-child input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source']",
          "content": "In query row **B**, select **grafana-testdata-datasource**.",
          "doIt": false
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "noop",
          "content": "Set the **Scenario** to **CSV Content** and paste the following data:\n\n```\nhost,region,role\nweb-1,us-east,frontend\nweb-2,eu-west,api\nweb-3,us-east,backend\n```"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='data-testid RefreshPicker run button']",
          "content": "Click **Refresh** to execute both queries."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "You should see two separate result sets. Query A contains time-series CPU metrics with a `host` column. Query B contains a host-to-region mapping table. The `host` column is common to both — you'll JOIN on it later.\n\nIn the next milestone, you hide these base queries from the visualization."
    }
  ]
}
